One like = one opinion (+reason) about alternative and non-traditional medicine.

Took the @vgr bait to do a one-opinion-per-like personal challenge. https://t.co/BHHaJVUy1g

@vgr 1. Alternative and non-traditional medicine is largely quacks and net harmful practices. Just like mainstream medicine. The fundamental cause of both is the same: misaligned incentives. Outside antibiotics, vaccination and public sanitation, little works, alternative or not.

@vgr 2. Alternative and non-traditional medicine treatments for non-infectious diseases should be systematically analyzed and where potential harms are limited tested as rigorously as possible while maintaining a much as possible their structure. https://t.co/B2KMz7O5v3
